items.name: Warrior's Tale
explicitMods: 100% increased effect of Tattoos in Radius
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The story of a life, written in blood and ink.

items.name: Pandemonium Bliss
enchantMods: Added Small Passive Skills grant: 6% increased Mana Reservation Efficiency of Skills

Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +7% to Fire Resistance
Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +12 to Maximum Energy Shield
Added Small Passive Skills have 35% increased Effect
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Small, Medium or Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Militant Faith
explicitMods:
Carved to glorify 5253 new faithful converted by High Templar Dominus
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Templars
+2% to all Elemental Resistances per 10 Devotion
1% reduced Mana Cost of Skills per 10 Devotion
Historic
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the utmost faithful, but that conviction became oppression.

items.name: Unnatural Instinct
explicitMods: Allocated Small Passive Skills in Radius grant nothing
Grants all bonuses of Unallocated Small Passive Skills in Radius
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: "I don't know how I know,
I just know that I know."

items.name: Stormshroud
explicitMods: +15% to Lightning Resistance
Modifiers to Chance to Avoid being Shocked apply to all Elemental Ailments
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The true secret of the elements
is that all are one and the same.

items.name: Thread of Hope
implicitMods: Corrupted Blood cannot be inflicted on you
explicitMods: Only affects Passives in Large Ring
Passives in Radius can be Allocated without being connected to your tree
-16% to all Elemental Resistances
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Though we cannot touch; one thought, one wish, through centuries alone in darkness.

items.name: Dragon Curio
enchantMods: Added Small Passive Skills grant: 6% increased Mana Reservation Efficiency of Skills
explicitMods: Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +11 to Intelligence
Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +8% to Lightning Resistance
Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +15 to Maximum Energy Shield
Added Small Passive Skills have 35% increased Effect
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Small, Medium or Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Voices
explicitMods: Adds 3 Jewel Socket Passive Skills
Adds 3 Small Passive Skills which grant nothing
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Only a madman would ignore a god's instructions.

items.name: Impossible Escape
explicitMods:
Passives in Radius of Wind Dancer can be Allocated
without being connected to your tree
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: She was the last of countless progeny bred to test the limits of limitless power.
In the cosmic prison of her birth, her siblings fought each other to the death
for supremacy. She alone reached her limit... and broke through.

items.name: The Balance of Terror
explicitMods: +15% to all Elemental Resistances
Action Speed cannot be Slowed below Base Value if you've cast Temporal Chains in the past 10 seconds
25% increased Cooldown Recovery Rate if you've cast Temporal Chains in the past 10 seconds
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Fellshrine stood as a holy bastion opposite the
Chamber of Sins, and all that it represented.
For one to rise, the other must fall.

items.name: Voices
explicitMods: Adds 3 Jewel Socket Passive Skills
Adds 1 Small Passive Skill which grants nothing
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Only a madman would ignore a god's instructions.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: 6% increased maximum Energy Shield
5% increased maximum Life
5% increased maximum Mana
+6% Chance to Block Attack Damage while affected by Determination
+28% to Critical Strike Multiplier while affected by Precision
You take 58% reduced Extra Damage from Critical Strikes while affected by Determination
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Melding of the Flesh
explicitMods: -71% to all Elemental Resistances
-4% to all maximum Elemental Resistances
Elemental Resistances are capped by your highest Maximum Elemental Resistance instead
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: "We awoke to a sudden jungle rupturing the valleys of our home.
Grasping limbs coiled around us, into us. We sank into each other,
then rose into the living sky. My family screams alongside me still."
